author: Josh Feldman
title: Debbie Wasserman Schultz: Trump Believes ‘He Was Elected as a Dictator’
text:
Debbie Wasserman Schultz: Trump Believes ‘He Was Elected as a Dictator’ by Josh Feldman | 5:14   video 
Congresswoman Debbie Wasserman Schultz today said that President Trump “believes he was elected as a dictator.” 
She praised Sally Yates on Fox Business Network today and cited this tweet to back up her “dictator” remark: When will the Democrats give us our Attorney General and rest of Cabinet! They should be ashamed of themselves! No wonder D.C. doesn't work! 
— Donald J. Trump (@realDonaldTrump) January 31, 2017 
She got into a heated back-and-forth with Bartiromo when the Fox anchor said Democrats are engaging in obstructoinism. 
Watch above, via Fox Business Network.
